16.0 Cancellation coverage
.br
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
Insurance sum: max. DKK 10,000 per person and max. DKK 50,000 per claim.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED
16.1 Coverage
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance coverage applies from the date on which the journey/deposit
was paid, up until the point when the insured commences the journey from
his/her country of residence.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
16.1.1 The insurance coverage applies if the journey cannot be completed
because the insured:
.of 5mm
*¤being hospitalised on account of an acute and serious illness or serious
injury
.of 5mm
*¤is dead
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤falls acutely ill or is seriously injured and, in the opinion of a
doctor, the journey would significantly exacerbate the illness or injury
or otherwise prove injurious to health
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤for medical reasons, cannot receive a vaccination that is suddenly
required for journeys to the destination in question. It is a condition
that the claim be made after the travel/deposit has been paid.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
16.1.2 The insurance also covers cancellation on account of the
insured's spouse/partner, children, children-in-law,
grandchildren, parents, parents' life partner, parents-in-law,
grandparents, siblings or siblings-in-law:
.of 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤expenses that the insured has paid for persons who are not covered by
the insurance. This also applies even if the insured has paid their
share of the travel.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤childbirth or consequences of pregnancy within one month of the forecast
date of birth
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤pregnancy issues in general
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤if the insured has declined medical treatment of an
illness/injury, or if medical treatment has been discontinued
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤if the insured's illness/injury was not in a good, stable phase
during the last two months before the travel/deposit was paid. In this
context, 'a good, stable phase' is taken to indicate that the
condition has been stationary without any kind of change, development
or periodical deterioration that has:
.of 10mm
¤*¤required contact with a doctor
.of 10mm
¤*¤resulted in changes to - or plans to adjust - treatment and/or
medication
.of 10mm
¤*¤resulted in the scheduling of additional examinations, treatment or
hospitalisation.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED
16.4 Reporting claims
:SKRSLUT
.br
In the event of a claim, the following documentation is to be submitted to
Privatsikring:
.of 5mm
*¤The demands from the travel organiser - documented in writing - together
with the terms and conditions for purchasing the travel.
.kp off
paid to cancel the journey, as well as previously paid expenses for
deposits, transport, rent of holiday residence etc.
.br
The insurance only covers sums that the insured has paid himself/herself.
.sp 3mm
If the reason for cancelling is not immediately obvious from the
documentation submitted, Privatsikring will determine whether insurance
coverage applies on the basis of the information presented.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
16.3 Exceptions
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance does not cover:
.br
.of 5mm
*¤if the travel/deposit was paid before this insurance came into effect
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤if the travel organiser was not informed of the cancellation immediately
after the occurrence of an event covered by the insurance
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤if the reason for cancellation existed when the travel was ordered or on
payment of the deposit
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤if the illness/injury or other reason for cancellation already existed
when the travel/deposit was paid
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤lost holiday purpose. This is taken to mean that the insured is affected
by a sudden illness or injury that prevents him/her from completing the
main activity planned for the holiday. For example, this may take the form
of an inner ear infection prior to a diving holiday, or a broken finger
prior to a golfing holiday.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤expenses that are reimbursed by the travel organiser
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤expenses for a doctor's note and/or other documentation
*¤being hospitalised on account of an acute and serious illness or serious
injury
.of 5mm
*¤suddenly dying.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
16.1.3 Moreover, the insurance will apply if the insured cannot travel on
account of the following:
.of 5mm
*¤Fire, burglary, storm, flood or explosion, resulting in significant
damage to the private residence or enterprise of the insured immediately
before the scheduled departure. A report from the police and/or rescue
company must be presented.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Fraudulent actions at the insured's own enterprise, perpetrated by an
employee or another person with operational links to the enterprise
immediately before the scheduled departure. A police report must be
presented.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Illegal work stoppage at the insured's own enterprise immediately before
the scheduled departure.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Involuntary dismissal of the insured in connection with full or
partial closure of an enterprise where the insured has been employed
full time - i.e. for at least 20 hours per week - for at least one year.
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤The Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Denmark discouraging travel to
the destination on account of war, natural disaster or similar. Payment
of compensation is conditional upon the decision to cancel
only being taken immediately before departure.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
16.2 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance covers the sum that the travel organiser may demand be
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Documentation for expenses paid for transport, rental of holiday
accommodation, planned activities etc. as well as documentation stating
that these expenses cannot be refunded.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Unused plane tickets, coach tickets and the like.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Doctor's note and copy of the patient journal that describes in detail
the treatment procedure and, if appropriate, death certificate, only in
the event of acute illness, injury or death.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Copy of police report only in the event of burglary, fire or
fraudulent actions.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Copy of report from rescue company only in the event of significant
damage as a result of fire, storm, flood or explosion.
.of
.sp 3mm
Expenses for doctor's notes and other documentation are to be covered by
the insured himself/herself.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
